reviewText: I enjoy this collection and watch them when I am in the mood for a good movie.  His wide acting range makes him a great entertainer and any of his movies good choices for a multi movie pack like this.

I had originally bought this set for Face/Off and Swordfish in particular. But as it turned out, the whole bundle is worth the money. Each movie has its own separate disc, instead of double-sided discs. But this is a 4-star review because Warner Bros broke the cardinal rule of DVD packaging: No stacking discs. It is a great collection nonetheless.
